{
  "stem": "11611.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the status for a long time in the Cold War.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Soviets had power and did what they pleased.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had power and we did as we pleased.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In other words, until such time as you have the elements of an international community with some of the apparatus of a-- of a bona fide institutional international community, you are not going to have any application of international law on a systematic basis.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You will have an application when a dominant power says now we want to enforce it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think some of it has happened now, but this is the primitive stage, where a dominant power says now we'll enforce it for other people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think in the current context of-- of world affairs, I'm not so sure my grandchildren will grow up and do a lot of thinking altogether.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two-- two principles were not covered at Nuremberg, one is indiscriminate air bombing is not a crime.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Technically it's a crime, but it's been engaged in endlessly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, German bombing and Allied bombing were not declared war crimes and those are two of the deadliest forms of warfare around.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Second, there is no bar to the use of nuclear weapons and there are more countries that have nuclear weapons.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, if you feel comfortable with the notion that this balance will always be maintained-- I do not because I think somewhere someone's going to slip up and a lot of nuclear bombs will go off.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't see that as a great future for mankind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In other words, I think the existing state of human affairs is dismal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was conscious that I was a Jew before, and I was conscious that I was a Jew afterwards.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
